JNI, SDK, NDK are all a nightmare to work with.
Here's some help in case you get stuck trying to build it.

https://wiki.debian.org/AndroidTools
https://packages.debian.org/sid/devel/google-android-ndk-installer

sudo apt-get install ia32-libs
sudo apt-get install libncurses5

`gradle build` may need to be run as sudo.

